      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances luxury with dependable performance. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seating surfaces remain supple and supportive, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been serviced at regular intervals with full synthetic oil, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires were replaced last season and have significant tread life remaining. It drives straight and true, with a smooth transmission and a responsive engine that shows no signs of hesitation. This is a complete, turn-key package for a buyer who values a car that has been treated with respect.",
